feat: major character tools overhaul with inpainting, style system, and UX polish

Character Page:
- Add Character Bible, Costume Director, Style Fusion, Environment Placement, and Preservation Lock sections with collapsible/toggleable/lockable/reorderable panels
- Add "Recreate image exactly" vs "Use image as inspiration" dropdown for extract mode
- Add extract target buttons (Identity, Attributes, Bible, Costume, Environment) to control which sections get populated
- Auto-enable extract targets when their corresponding section is turned ON
- Add Style Library dropdown for selecting style folders during generation
- Add Prompt Preview section showing the full outgoing prompt
- Add draggable section reordering with "Set Active Layout as Default" persistence
- Wire all enabled sections (attributes, bible, costume, fusion, environment, preservation) into generation prompts
- Enforce A-pose and flat background rules in backend prompt engineering
- Default Preservation Lock toggles to unchecked

Image Viewer & Inpainting:
- Add full inpainting toolbar (Brush, Eraser, Marquee, Lasso, Smart Select, Smart Erase, Outpaint, Remove BG, Style Transfer)
- Wire all inpainting tools to Gemini API with ref image and style context support
- Add visual brush size circle for brush, eraser, and smart erase
- Reset to normal cursor after applying any inpainting action
- Allow zoom/pan while image is generating (only block drawing tools)
- Hard-threshold alpha in Remove Background for clean cutouts
- Rewrite Outpaint to send two images for seamless scene extension
- Add per-image edit history with disk persistence and "Are you sure?" clear confirmation
- Add image shape label (Portrait/Landscape/Square) to resolution display

Shell & Navigation:
- Replace native Electron menu bar with in-app File/Edit dropdown menus
- Add File menu: Save/Open Session, Set/Reset Save Folder, Reset App
- Add Session Templates dropdown for saving/loading tool presets
- Add Style Library page with three-column folder/image/guidance layout
- Remove sidebar auto-collapse on mouse leave (manual button only)

Backend:
- Add editor API routes (inpaint, smart-select, smart-erase, outpaint, remove-bg, style-transfer)
- Add styles API routes for Style Library CRUD
- Add system routes for Photoshop integration, cache clearing, save folder management
- Add recreate_mode flag to character generation for exact visual matching
- Expand extraction prompts with detailed attribute instructions and environment fields
- Fix circular import with cancel.py module

UX Polish:
- Fix unicode escape characters showing literally in tooltips across all pages
- Add subtle focus border for text inputs (no flash)
- Add hover brightness effect on section cards
- Add section ON/OFF toggles with middle-click support and dimming
- Add lock icons (SVG) to prevent AI from overwriting locked sections
- Disable inputs during generation; add pulsing button animation for API calls
- Add clipboard paste support via Electron IPC
- Add XML export modal, number stepper, color field with eyedropper
- Add context menu improvements and tab prompt editing
